OL,3,CWhat happens now that Andy Burnham has
OL,4,Cwon the Makerfield by-election?
OL,6,FAndy Burnham has won the Makerfield by-
OL,7,Felection with more than half of the
OL,8,Fvote, opening the door to challenge
OL,9,FSir Keir Starmer for the leadership.
OL,11,FIn his victory speech on Friday,
OL,12,FBurnham described his win as a
OL,13,F"turning point" for the party, while
OL,14,Fhe pledged not to use the constituency
OL,15,Fas a stepping stone.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
