OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781874674
OL,3,CWhat happens now that Andy Burnham has
OL,4,Cwon the Makerfield by-election?
OL,6,FHowever, Burnham has consistently
OL,7,Fpolled as the most popular candidate
OL,8,Ffor leadership of the Labour Party,
OL,9,Fand allies now believe his victory
OL,10,Fgives him a huge vote of confidence to
OL,11,Fchallenge the increasingly unpopular
OL,12,FStarmer.
OL,14,FBut how would Burnham trigger a
OL,15,Fleadership contest, and how long would
OL,16,Fit take? ITV News explains.
OL,18,FWhat does Burnham need to do before he
OL,19,Fcan launch a leadership challenge?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781874674
OL,3,CWhat happens now that Andy Burnham has
OL,4,Cwon the Makerfield by-election?
OL,6,FBefore triggering any sort of
OL,7,Fleadership challenge, Burnham needs to
OL,8,Fstep down from his role as Mayor of
OL,9,FGreater Manchester.
OL,11,FUnder Labour Party rules, MPs cannot
OL,12,Fhave multiple jobs, so they can focus
OL,13,Fon serving their constituency instead.
OL,15,FOnce Burnham stands down, which could
OL,16,Fbe as early as Monday, a by-election
OL,17,Fwill be triggered to elect a new Mayor
OL,18,Fof Greater Manchester.
OL,20,FHow does a leadership challenge work?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781874674
OL,3,CWhat happens now that Andy Burnham has
OL,4,Cwon the Makerfield by-election?
OL,6,FCurrent Labour rules state that to
OL,7,Fmount a leadership contest, 20% of the
OL,8,Fparty's MPs ` or 81 colleagues ` need
OL,9,Fto back a candidate first.
OL,11,FBurnham's allies have said he already
OL,12,Fhas the numbers required to do this.
OL,14,FOnce the leadership contest is
OL,15,Ftriggered, other candidates can join
OL,16,Fthe race if they also have the backing
OL,17,Fof at least 81 MPs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
