OL,3,CWhat happens now that Andy Burnham has
OL,4,Cwon the Makerfield by-election?
OL,6,FStarmer, however, will automatically
OL,7,Fbe on the ballot paper. He would also
OL,8,Fcontinue in the role while the contest
OL,9,Fwas in progress.
OL,11,FOn Friday morning, the PM confirmed
OL,12,Fthat he will run against Burnham if he
OL,13,Ftriggers a contest.
OL,15,FHe said: "If there is a contest, just
OL,16,Fto be clear with you, then yes, I will
OL,17,Frun, I will stand and I've said
OL,18,Frepeatedly I'm not going to walk away
OL,19,Ffrom that."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
