OL,3,CWhat happens now that Andy Burnham has
OL,4,Cwon the Makerfield by-election?
OL,6,FIn Labour's 126-year history, there
OL,7,Fhas never been an official leadership
OL,8,Fchallenge mounted against a sitting
OL,9,Fprime minister.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FHow long until we can expect a
OL,17,Fchallenge?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
