FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781874674
OL,3,CWhat happens now that Andy Burnham has
OL,4,Cwon the Makerfield by-election?
OL,6,FAnother challenge facing those wanting
OL,7,Fto unseat Starmer is the deadline that
OL,8,Fmay be imposed by the NEC.
OL,10,FMPs will likely only have around a
OL,11,Fmonth to shore up their supporters.
OL,13,FIt is thought that Burnham will talk
OL,14,Fto Starmer over the weekend,
OL,15,Fencouraging him to step aside rather
OL,16,Fthan fight the contest.
OL,18,FIf he does not stand down, then
OL,19,FBurnham may trigger the contest early
OL,20,Fnext week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
