OL,3,CWhat happens now that Andy Burnham has
OL,4,Cwon the Makerfield by-election?
OL,6,FWithin a week, we could have the
OL,7,Fbeginnings of a leadership contest
OL,8,Fwhich could run throughout the summer,
OL,9,Flikely to conclude before the Labour
OL,10,FParty conference at the end of
OL,11,FSeptember.
OL,13,FITV News Digital Political Reporter
OL,14,FLewis Denison explains: How quickly
OL,15,Fcould Andy Burnham become PM?
OL,17,FWho gets to vote?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
