OL,3,CWhat happens now that Andy Burnham has
OL,4,Cwon the Makerfield by-election?
OL,6,FFailing that, the candidate who places
OL,7,Flast is eliminated, and the voters who
OL,8,Fput them as their number one choice
OL,9,Fwill have their votes moved to their
OL,10,Fsecond choice candidate.
OL,12,FThe process continues until one
OL,13,Fcandidate secures more than 50% of the
OL,14,Fvotes cast.
OL,16,FWhy is a union vote important?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
