OL,3,CWhat happens now that Andy Burnham has
OL,4,Cwon the Makerfield by-election?
OL,6,FLabour as a political party is
OL,7,Fformally linked to several trade
OL,8,Funions such as Unite the Union,
OL,9,FUnison, and GMB. Each provides
OL,10,Ffunding, campaign support, activists
OL,11,Fand as a result has sway over policy.
OL,13,FLeadership candidates often rely on
OL,14,Fthe resources provided by unions,
OL,15,Fmaking them one of the most important
OL,16,Fstakeholders in a Labour leadership
OL,17,Fcontest.
OL,19,FWho else might be in the running?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
