OL,3,CWhat happens now that Andy Burnham has
OL,4,Cwon the Makerfield by-election?
OL,6,FIt's not just the new Makerfield MP
OL,7,Fwho might be in the running for this
OL,8,Fcontest.
OL,10,FFormer Health Secretary Wes Streeting
OL,11,Fhas previously said he will run for
OL,12,Fleadership, but waited to allow
OL,13,FBurnham the chance to join the race.
OL,15,FAfter resigning in May, Streeting said
OL,16,Frushing into a leadership role without
OL,17,Fgiving Burnham the chance "would lack
OL,18,Fthe legitimacy".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
