OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781874674
OL,3,CWhat happens now that Andy Burnham has
OL,4,Cwon the Makerfield by-election?
OL,6,FHe said a contest without Burnham
OL,7,F"wasn't in the parties interests and
OL,8,Fwasn't in the national interest".
OL,10,FOther potential candidates include
OL,11,Fformer Deputy Leader Angela Rayner,
OL,12,FEnergy Secretary Ed Miliband and
OL,13,Fformer Armed Forces Minister Al Carns.
OL,15,FLabour has never elected a woman as
OL,16,Fleader, and it looks increasingly
OL,17,Finevitable they still won't.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
